  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-PROV-01 adversarial sample)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This package contains a provenance chain in which an intermediate synthesis node has no upstream provenance edge and is not marked as foundational evidence, triggering W-PROV-01.",
