      "uofa:isFoundationalEvidence": true,
      "description": "Particle image velocimetry measurements of the FDA generic centrifugal pump internal flow field at 2500 RPM and 6 L/min, collected at the FDA White Oak laboratory. Used as foundational experimental evidence for velocity field validation."
    }
